## Trait Definitions

### Stage 1: Retriever

```rust
#[async_trait]
pub trait Retriever: Send + Sync {
    /// Identifier for metrics attribution and eval benchmarking.
    fn name(&self) -> &str;

    /// Retrieve entries relevant to a query within a scope.
    async fn retrieve(
        &self,
        query: &str,
        scope_id: &str,
        opts: &RetrievalOpts,
    ) -> Result<RetrievalResult>;
}
```


### Stage 2: Augmenter

```rust
pub trait Augmenter: Send + Sync {
    /// Identifier for metrics attribution and eval benchmarking.
    fn name(&self) -> &str;

    /// Format search results into a context string for LLM consumption.
    fn augment(
        &self,
        query: &str,
        results: &[SearchResult],
        budget: &TokenBudget,
    ) -> Result<AugmentedContext>;
}
```
